<lyrics>[V1]
 Vawlei cung sualnak vialte kha, A thiang thi in a tawi dih cang,
 Pathian Fa thangthat hmu ko seh, Sualnak khan a kan khamh dih cang, Lam
 kan tlau ca ah harnak le, Sifah retheih kan huat na in, Kan sualnak kha
 kan tawlpiak tuah, Hawhra bangin kan thianter tuah.

[C1]
   Hawhra rang nakin, Kan thianter deuh tuah, Na thi in na kan tawl ah
   cun, (tawl ahcun) Hawhra nakin kan thiang deuh lai (deuh lai)

[V2]
 Pathian fa hling luchin an chinh, Vailamtahnak kha an put ter,
 Ngaihchiat sifahnak kha a in, Siseh law sawhsawh a si lo, Keimah sualnak
 thianter awk ah, Na thihnak hmun ah ka hruai tuah. Hawhra nakin ka thian
 nakhnga, A thiang na thi in ka tawl tuah.

[C2]
   Hawhra rang nakin, Kan thianter deuh tuah, Na thi in na kan tawl ah
   cun, (tawl ahcun) Hawhra nakin kan thiang deuh lai (deuh lai)

[V3]
 Khamhbawi keimah lam ka tlau cang, Ka sualnak kha a tam ca ah, Ka
 lungchung sualnak a khah ca'h, Ti nih a thianter kho lai lo, Jesuh
 biakamnak kha ka zumh, Na thi thletnak ah ka kal lai. Hawhra bangin ka
 thian nakhnga, Na lianhnak in ka thianter tuah.

[C3]
   Hawhra rang nakin, Kan thianter deuh tuah, Na thi in na kan tawl ah
   cun, (tawl ahcun) Hawhra nakin kan thiang deuh lai (deuh lai)</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>TUUFA THISEN CH127</title>
</song>